{"tid":2283212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"比陳雲笑死！！","createTime":"2020-11-12T11:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T15:08:34.000Z","uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"467d9f106333d543b0e38b341ab3b1e024b68c1a","tid":2283212,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"陳雲：由於季節性流感的殺傷力遠比covid-19要高，我呼籲港府即刻採取比covid-19更為嚴厲的防疫措施：馬上封城罷市罷課六個月至明年夏天安全期，關閉港口及機場，並停止一切不必要的公共服務及商業活動，郵遞服務即刻全部停止，速遞服務高危要即刻停止，食物遞送服務高危要即刻停止，地鐵及巴士絕對高危要全部停開，以保障香港市民的生命。<br />\n至於殯儀業，必須加緊工作，尤其是要準備足夠棺材。<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩戴到落棺材<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ee86851694dbb8374bcb3e86e55111b5069c33","tid":2283212,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">扮燒山fans嘅雲糞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0vOfJ0.jpg&h=d9a57d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGVnkaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGVnkaG.jpg&h=22e80bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8K3j6QH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8K3j6QH.jpg&h=bc059408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsF24Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsF24Co.jpg&h=1fa7a04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ec3Rf7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEc3Rf7Z.jpg&h=32b72de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjOawGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjOawGh.jpg&h=38dce965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBxbf7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src